* Repair Tax Incentive (Sweden):
**[https://data.riksdagen.se/fil/201F2375-45FE-4A3A-BEB9-42B089E99A93 From Value Chain to Value Cycle] (in Swedish and English): The Swedish government is introducing tax breaks (halving VAT) on repairs.

* Right to Repair (EU - in development):
** [http://www.europarl.europa.eu/sides/getDoc.do?pubRef=-//EP//TEXT+REPORT+A8-2017-0214+0+DOC+XML+V0//EN On a Longer Lifetime for Products]: Benefits for Consumers and Companies (report outlining proposed legislation): The EU is preparing legislation that would legalise a customer's 'right to repair', and would force vendors to design products for longer life and easier maintenance.

